definitions.text:
@gặp may
* adj
- to be lucky; in luck's way

@gặp nhau
* verb
-to meet

@gặng
- (cũng nói gặng hỏi) Question closely (until one gets an answer...)
=gặng mãi nó mới chịu nói+He only spoke after a very close questioning

@gặp nạn
* adjective
-to be in danger

@gặp mặt
* verb
- to meet, to see

@gặp gỡ
* verb
- to meet with

@gặp phải
- Meet with (difficulties, bad luck...)
=Không gặp phải khó khăn thì đã xong việc rồi+If he has not met with difficulties, he would have done hia job
